      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not planning on getting drunk or anything, just a tiny bit of wine to help with the anxiety so i can actually fall asleep. i've heard from some people that the alcohol helps the diazepam work faster. is there really a big difference between taking it alone vs with just a single glass? it seems like it would just make the relaxation effect better.",
